items.title: Seven dead after migrant boat sinks near Thai-Malaysian border
items.description: Hundreds of Rohingyas, who fled Myanmar in hopes of a better life in Malaysia, remain missing.

items.title: Dozens of inmates found hanged in Ecuador prison
